-- Hermes Says 2010 Revenue May Advance 15%, Operating Margin Will Increase
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-11-09T06:36:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/hermes-says-2010-revenue-may-advance-15-operating-margin-will-increase.html
Hermes International said that full-
year sales may rise about 15 percent excluding currency
movements.  The full-year underlying operating margin may rise by one
or two percentage points, the company said in a statement on its
website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
